summary: This file defines a Vue component for rendering an SVG icon representing support.
functionality: The main functionality of this file is to provide a reusable SVG icon component that can be used throughout the project to represent support.
relationships: This component can be imported and used in other Vue components where a support icon is needed, such as in a help section or support page.

identified_relationships.description: The IconSupport component is likely referenced in the index.html file to be included in the main application.
The IconSupport component might be configured or included in the build process through vite.config.js.
The IconSupport component may use Tailwind CSS classes defined in tailwind.config.js for styling.
